Gravity-Well
.author
Gary Teachout 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
A celestial motion simulator that simulates the motion of up to twenty
bodies in a Newtonian universe.  The view of the simulation may be scaled,
rotated in three dimensions or repositioned.  
